Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.09,0:01:15.54,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}僕らはできないことだって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.73,0:01:17.76,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}きっとできるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.76,0:01:20.75,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}君と一緒なら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.49,0:00:06.86,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}未來之事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.86,0:00:09.11,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}誰人能得見
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.43,0:00:12.13,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}誰人能知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.58,0:00:16.15,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}似朝霧沉沉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.38,0:00:20.72,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}將熹光籠罩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.71,0:00:24.87,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}奇蹟之事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.47,0:00:27.56,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}將由誰創造
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.75,0:00:30.05,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}無人能定調
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.87,0:00:34.40,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}在磚瓦路上奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.76,0:00:38.20,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}於思考之前出招
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.39,0:00:40.44,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}我的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.44,0:00:42.44,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}渾身上下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.88,0:00:48.11,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}都在奮力呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.11,0:00:50.55,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}因僅憑一顆心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.55,0:00:52.70,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}拚盡全力生息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.70,0:00:56.24,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}苦痛纏身在即
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.55,0:00:59.69,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}只要踏出一步
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.69,0:01:01.79,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}世界就會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:04.23,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}想像外的笑顏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.23,0:01:06.49,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}也能現於眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.49,0:01:08.76,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}只需相信便好
